\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mnr7uwis17aj\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">马学军认为家装的局部环节已经没得做了，他想用「端到端」的模式再造一次。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"101307424\" data-ratio=\"0.08888888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"900\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d266c885&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQDFNHs0vUhrvC75JRXlG0rM2iat53EoZMsodUxkMSYWXNSIFUEeuo2I89A9ibZcCic1oNlHEWLAxeWpFZgeic0wdtg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"25\" data-imgfileid=\"101307425\" data-ratio=\"0.024074074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"height: 14px;width: 578px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aedec240&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FQicyPhNHD5vagBvpJSWBnNYW2D0LereibplkrJOvk6R1Efiaq0NlWibAtLj0DDlMWGggbQ9KdrLibUvZbz91W4FNd7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: right;visibility: visible